name: Red Rocks Stage Day 2 50k
description:
I think everyone got lost at some point. I missed the short out and back to the aid station at Yavapai Vista (3rd aid station stop). Ran that part out of order but meant I had a 12 mile section without aid and ran out of food/water. 

To clarify, I was never really lost (I put many of the trail signs up at the junctions a decade ago), I just had no idea which way the course was.
